{
  "texts": [
    "Most articles were published in \"Computers and Education: Artificial Intelligence and Expert Systems with Applications.\"",
    "Notably, studies utilizing multiple AI algorithms aim to construct models predicting students' learning patterns or performance.",
    "This trend highlights the increasing integration of AI technology in educational research to enhance operational efficiency.The inclusion of papers from diverse nations provides Nigeria with a global perspective, allowing valuable insights.",
    "\"Profiling and prediction,\" \"adaptive systems with personalization,\" and intelligent tutoring systems emerge as impactful contributors to AI, aligning with earlier research on academic challenges.",
    "While less common, simulation annealing and search and optimization are employed, with the prevailing trend involving the use of two or more AI algorithms to predict learners' success in online learning environments."
  ]
}